er Essentials Plus certification. The second part of the book presents a selection of additional resources that are available to help you implement the controls or become certified.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Apr 2024) 0aComputer security. 7aCOMPUTERS / Security / General.2bisacsh  aCREST.  acyber essentials plus.  acyber essentials requirements.  acyber essentials scheme.  acyber security.  ainformation security.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertSciendo All Ebooks Trial Collection 2024z97831115024960 cEPUBz978178778436940uhttps://sciendo.com/book/9781787784352  a978-3-11-150249-6  Sciendo All Ebooks Trial Collection 2024b2024  aGBV-deGruyter-alles